data.description: Look no further!  These 5 beds 4 baths are an absolute must see.  Everything you are looking for and more!!  Beautiful hardwood flooring along with stunning plantation shutters. Open kitchen concept complete with granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances. Master bedroom located privately on the main floor with deck access and isolated full bath with walk-in closet.  While everything you will need including a laundry room, full bath, and additional bedroom is on the main floor, the top floor boasts 3 generously sized bedrooms with full bathroom.  And if that isn't enough, this house offers a fully finished basement with 2 bonus rooms, entertainment room, work out room, bar area, and full bath.  Conveniently located near I-20 and Chapel Hill Rd. and minutes from shopping. *** I am an agent and this is my home.
